Step 2: Understand Field Types
Key Scapy field types you'll use:

ByteField: 1-byte integer (0-255)
ShortField: 2-byte integer
IntField: 4-byte integer
XIntField/XShortField: Hex display variants
StrField: Variable-length string
StrFixedLenField: Fixed-length string
ByteEnumField: Byte with enumerated values
